            "DialogCategory": 8,
            "DialogCondition": 0,
            "GroupId": 5,
            "ActionName": "",
            "DialogType": 0,
            "Duration": 11460,
            "LocalizeKR": "'파르페'……\n완벽한 요리를요.",
            "LocalizeJP": "「パフェ」……完璧なお料理を。",
